messages.ssml: <speak>According to the World Health Organization, the likelihood of an infected person contaminating commercial goods is low and the risk of catching the virus that causes <sub alias="covid 19">COVID-19</sub> from a package that has been moved, travelled, and exposed to different conditions and temperature is also low.</speak>
